<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>Activ Radar - Εισαγωγή Νέου Αθλητικού Κέντρου</title>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<!-- STYLE CSS -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="includes/css/style.css">
		<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
		<!-- CDNs -->
		<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" id="bootstrap-css">
		<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="includes/js/angular.min.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="includes/js/angular-route.min.js"></script>
		<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/angular-inview/3.0.0/angular-inview.min.js"></script>
		<script src="includes/controllers/activities.js"></script>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-select/1.13.2/css/bootstrap-select.min.css">
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.7.5/angular-cookies.min.js"></script>
		<!-- Latest compiled and minified JavaScript -->
		<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-select/1.13.2/js/bootstrap-select.min.js"></script>
		<!-- Scripts -->
		<script src="includes/js/dynamicfields.js"></script>
		<!-- favicon display -->
		<link rel="shortcut icon" href="includes/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
		<link rel="icon" href="includes/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
	</head>
	<body ng-app="myApp" ng-controller="ActivitiesController" style="background-image: url('includes/images/athletes.jpg'); background-position: center;
		background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover;">
		<br>
		<br>
		
		<header>
			<%- include('./includes/html/nav_logged.ejs'); %>
		</header>
		<div class="wrapper">
			
			<div class="inner">
				<form class="needs-validation" novalidate  ng-init="get_sportcenters()" ng-submit="post_sportscenter()">
					<h3>ΕΙΣΑΓΩΓΗ ΝEOY ΑΘΛΗΤΙΚΟΥ ΚΕΝΤΡΟΥ</h3>
					<h5>Συμπλήρωσε τα πεδία για να εισάγεις νέο αθλητικό κέντρο</h5>
					<div class="container">
						<div class="row">
							<label for="sportsCenter">Αθλητικό κέντρο</label>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<input type="text" placeholder="Όνομα αθλητικού κέντρου" class="form-control" ng-model="Sportscenter.name" id="spor_name">
							<div class="invalid-feedback">
								Εισάγετε όνομα (υποχρεωτικό πεδίο)
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<input type="text" placeholder="Διεύθυνση" class="form-control" ng-model="Sportscenter.address" id="spor_address">
							<div class="invalid-feedback">
								Εισάγετε διεύθυνση (υποχρεωτικό πεδίο)
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<input type="text" placeholder="Ιστοσελίδα" class="form-control" ng-model="Sportscenter.webpage" id="spor_webpage">
							<div class="invalid-feedback">
								Εισάγετε ιστοσελίδα (υποχρεωτικό πεδίο)
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<label for="spor_category">Κατηγορίες δραστηριοτήτων:</label>
						</div>
						<div class="row" id="category_spor">
							<select id="spor_category" class="selectpicker" multiple class="form-control" ng-init="activity_category">
								<option value="team">{{activity_category.op1}}</option>
								<option value="solo">{{activity_category.op2}}</option>
								<option value="fight">{{activity_category.op3}}</option>
								<option value="dance">{{activity_category.op4}}</option>
								<option value="water">{{activity_category.op5}}</option>
								<option value="inside">{{activity_category.op6}}</option>
								<option value="outside">{{activity_category.op7}}</option>
								<option value="ice">{{activity_category.op8}}</option>
							</select>
							<div class="invalid-feedback">
								Επιλέξτε μία ή περισσότερες κατηγορίες (υποχρεωτικό πεδίο)
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
							<button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Υποβολή</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>
		<%- include('./includes/html/footer.ejs'); %>
	</body>
</html>